articles.author: Lori Dillon, The Associated Press
articles.title: Joseph Corcoran executed in Indiana - WANE
articles.description: The Indiana Department of Corrections executed convicted murderer Joseph Corcoran early Wednesday morning.
articles.content:
MICHIGAN CITY, Ind. (WANE) — The Indiana Department of Corrections executed convicted murderer Joseph Corcoran early Wednesday morning.
